1
00:00:12,208 --> 00:00:14,916
The final location is Golden Lake Plaza.

2
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:18,833
One last step
and you'll make the headlines tomorrow.

3
00:00:27,458 --> 00:00:29,500
GOLDEN LAKE PLAZA

4
00:00:33,375 --> 00:00:34,541
Fuck you, Wu Tien-chi.

5
00:00:41,875 --> 00:00:45,125
Yu-ching, Daddy's coming for you.

6
00:00:45,833 --> 00:00:46,750
Wang Cheng-nan!

7
00:00:48,916 --> 00:00:51,375
Stay away from me! Stay away.

8
00:00:51,458 --> 00:00:52,291
Okay.

9
00:00:52,375 --> 00:00:54,791
-Stay away from me.
-Calm down.

10
00:00:55,333 --> 00:00:57,166
Don't do anything stupid. Come down.

11
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:59,666
I'm sick of this corrupt world.

12
00:00:59,750 --> 00:01:02,041
The cops are useless fools too.

13
00:01:03,166 --> 00:01:05,375
I only need to jump.

14
00:01:05,458 --> 00:01:09,125
It'll go viral online and the police
will have to take her death seriously.

15
00:01:09,208 --> 00:01:11,958
Listen, we don't know
if it's Wang Yu-ching yet.

16
00:01:12,041 --> 00:01:14,750
We'll find the culprit soon.
There's still hope.

17
00:01:15,541 --> 00:01:17,791
-Come down.
-Stay away from me.

18
00:01:19,583 --> 00:01:20,458
I killed someone.

19
00:01:21,083 --> 00:01:23,041
I killed that bastard.

20
00:01:23,791 --> 00:01:28,041
-Chao, Wang Cheng-nan is going to jump.
-DNA confirms it wasn't Wang Yu-ching.

21
00:01:28,125 --> 00:01:31,083
We've got a new lead on his daughter.
Stop him now.

22
00:01:31,166 --> 00:01:33,083
Fuck you, Wu Tien-chi.

23
00:01:33,166 --> 00:01:36,250
That guy isn't dead. He's in hospital.
You didn't kill anyone.

24
00:01:36,333 --> 00:01:38,041
So don't do anything stupid.

25
00:01:38,125 --> 00:01:41,375
You're all lying to me.

26
00:01:42,208 --> 00:01:43,625
My daughter is dead.

27
00:01:44,125 --> 00:01:45,541
I killed someone.

28
00:01:45,625 --> 00:01:46,958
It's too late.

29
00:01:47,041 --> 00:01:48,333
-Too late.
-Wang Cheng-nan!

30
00:01:58,583 --> 00:02:00,333
I tried to kill myself once.

31
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:04,833
I wanted it all to be over.

32
00:02:08,458 --> 00:02:09,750
But trust me.

33
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:14,166
You'll regret it afterwards.

34
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,833
I guarantee it.

35
00:02:22,041 --> 00:02:26,750
Think about your daughter.
What will happen to her if you die?

36
00:02:30,708 --> 00:02:32,125
-Yu-ching.
-Come down.

37
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,750
Wait!

38
00:02:38,833 --> 00:02:40,958
She's alive! The DNA results are back.

39
00:02:41,041 --> 00:02:42,291
It's not your daughter.

40
00:02:43,291 --> 00:02:44,125
Don't jump.

41
00:02:48,708 --> 00:02:49,750
Hey!

42
00:03:16,916 --> 00:03:21,916
AGENT FROM ABOVE

43
00:03:22,958 --> 00:03:26,958
THE DESCENT

44
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:53,500
-Call an ambulance!
-Abductee found. Send an ambulance.

45
00:03:53,583 --> 00:03:56,250
-All units, abductee found.
-Get ready to clear a route.

46
00:03:56,333 --> 00:03:57,416
Wang Yu-ching.

47
00:03:58,291 --> 00:03:59,250
Wang Yu-ching!

48
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:15,041
The guy you stabbed
wasn't fatally wounded.

49
00:04:15,125 --> 00:04:16,958
He's been moved out of ICU.

50
00:04:21,708 --> 00:04:23,416
Hey. Wipe your hands.

51
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,125
Yu-ching.

52
00:05:00,916 --> 00:05:03,250
I'm here now.

53
00:05:24,875 --> 00:05:26,000
Wait a moment.

54
00:05:28,958 --> 00:05:30,583
Here. Take this.

55
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:35,291
-Sister Lo.
-What?

56
00:05:35,375 --> 00:05:37,333
You really won't leave?

57
00:05:38,125 --> 00:05:40,333
I want to stay here. You should go.

58
00:05:40,416 --> 00:05:44,500
Remember to eat properly. Got it?

59
00:05:53,041 --> 00:05:55,833
-Try not to miss me too much.
-I'm sure I'll get by.

60
00:06:34,875 --> 00:06:35,708
Sis.

61
00:06:42,666 --> 00:06:46,625
You've been hiding from me for so long.
You finally came to see me?

62
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:57,125
I was staying away,

63
00:06:57,750 --> 00:07:00,916
in the hope you'd forget about me
and move on.

64
00:07:02,708 --> 00:07:04,375
I thought that with time,

65
00:07:05,375 --> 00:07:06,791
you'd start to get over it.

66
00:07:07,708 --> 00:07:11,458
But it's been two years
and you still can't let me go.

67
00:07:14,791 --> 00:07:16,083
Stop being such a crybaby.

68
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:19,375
And stop repeating my name
each morning like it's a sutra.

69
00:07:19,458 --> 00:07:20,625
It drives me nuts.

70
00:07:21,291 --> 00:07:24,375
Are you kidding? I'll never forget you.

71
00:07:25,875 --> 00:07:27,125
Idiot.

72
00:07:28,958 --> 00:07:30,875
I was never the smartest kid.

73
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:44,208
Sis, I pray every day to the gods
to keep you safe and sound.

74
00:07:44,708 --> 00:07:48,458
How can I rest in peace
never knowing if you're safe?

75
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:53,250
Do as Chieh says
and leave Dongfeng Market.

76
00:07:55,208 --> 00:07:56,666
I can't just leave you here.

77
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:59,000
You're an earth-bound spirit.
You can't leave.

78
00:07:59,083 --> 00:08:01,416
It's not like we just
became ghosts yesterday.

79
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:04,541
And the Third Crown Prince's
agent from above has our back.

80
00:08:04,625 --> 00:08:06,125
He won't let anyone hurt us.

81
00:08:08,166 --> 00:08:10,666
Will you come back and see me again?

82
00:08:13,208 --> 00:08:14,833
If you promise me one thing.

83
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:16,166
What?

84
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:21,458
Get used to life without me.

85
00:08:24,958 --> 00:08:27,250
And then get on with your life.

86
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:34,083
Don't think about me too much. Just…

87
00:08:34,583 --> 00:08:35,875
Just every now and again.

88
00:08:41,541 --> 00:08:42,541
If…

89
00:08:43,583 --> 00:08:45,166
If fate permits it…

90
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,291
we'll meet here again.

91
00:08:58,166 --> 00:08:59,000
Okay.

92
00:09:00,666 --> 00:09:02,125
I'll leave tomorrow.

93
00:09:25,416 --> 00:09:27,083
That was close.

94
00:09:28,916 --> 00:09:31,083
Yeah, good thing we pulled him back.

95
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:36,375
Go ahead.

96
00:09:38,666 --> 00:09:39,500
Yes.

97
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,166
Okay.

98
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,291
Okay, got it.

99
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:46,083
Fuck.

100
00:09:46,166 --> 00:09:47,875
Some guy who'd lost all his money

101
00:09:47,958 --> 00:09:50,833
jumped off a building
near the one Wang Cheng-nan was at.

102
00:09:51,458 --> 00:09:54,125
-What was the time of death?
-Around an hour ago.

103
00:09:55,041 --> 00:09:56,250
This is the deceased.

104
00:09:59,375 --> 00:10:00,708
GENDER: MALE

105
00:10:02,833 --> 00:10:04,166
The elevator's broken.

106
00:10:04,875 --> 00:10:06,458
Am I really doomed?

107
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:27,708
-That bastard had a backup plan.
-Fuck.

108
00:10:27,791 --> 00:10:31,291
The magic array is complete.
He's channeling the Demon King's spirit.

109
00:11:53,708 --> 00:11:58,000
I finally made it up here.

110
00:12:08,625 --> 00:12:10,125
The full moon is tomorrow.

111
00:12:11,875 --> 00:12:13,500
The battlefield is Dongfeng Market.

112
00:12:15,791 --> 00:12:18,625
Fuck. Is this Stranger Things?

113
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,041
Han Chieh.

114
00:13:16,833 --> 00:13:19,666
-Everyone's left. Why haven't you?
-The ghosts are still here.

115
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,875
I got snacks for Hsiao-ming
and the grannies.

116
00:13:24,125 --> 00:13:26,458
I'm going to get some weapons from Fu.
Go home.

117
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,958
Tonight's the showdown, isn't it?

118
00:13:33,208 --> 00:13:34,291
Yes.

119
00:13:34,375 --> 00:13:36,916
Can I tag along today?
Just during the daytime.

120
00:13:40,416 --> 00:13:42,833
It's a free world. Do as you please.

121
00:13:42,916 --> 00:13:45,583
There's somewhere I want to go.
Can you come with me?

122
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:09,791
After I got sick,

123
00:14:09,875 --> 00:14:14,208
I started coming here to clear my head
and wish upon this tree.

124
00:14:39,541 --> 00:14:42,875
It's become a ritual.
I always finish with a prayer.

125
00:14:50,333 --> 00:14:51,291
All done.

126
00:14:53,291 --> 00:14:56,125
-What did you wish for?
-World peace.

127
00:15:00,916 --> 00:15:03,875
-You really think this works?
-I do.

128
00:15:03,958 --> 00:15:05,333
The old guard told me

129
00:15:05,416 --> 00:15:07,666
that magic can't overcome divine power,

130
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:11,000
divine power can't overcome karma
and karma can't overcome willpower.

131
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:15,166
So someone with a wish
is even stronger than Doctor Strange.

132
00:15:15,791 --> 00:15:18,833
You really think a wish
can bring about world peace?

133
00:15:20,208 --> 00:15:21,333
You never know.

134
00:15:21,833 --> 00:15:25,083
My love for the world
is woven into that wish.

135
00:15:42,541 --> 00:15:43,541
If it makes you happy.

136
00:15:44,416 --> 00:15:45,708
Make a wish too.

137
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,833
-I don't want to.
-Just one.

138
00:15:53,416 --> 00:15:55,750
Hey, just make one wish.

139
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:03,291
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT
CENTRAL DISTRICT PRECINCT

140
00:16:16,375 --> 00:16:17,416
Come on.

141
00:16:19,916 --> 00:16:21,666
We need to be ready.

142
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:27,583
GOLDEN BRICK

143
00:16:58,291 --> 00:17:00,750
FUCK YOU AND DIE DEMON KING

144
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:04,416
Han Chieh, will this really work?

145
00:17:05,291 --> 00:17:07,166
Works with ghosts, why not demons?

146
00:17:07,958 --> 00:17:10,166
Give me a hand. There's a lot to write.

147
00:17:17,458 --> 00:17:18,333
GO BACK TO HELL

148
00:17:38,041 --> 00:17:39,208
All done over there?

149
00:17:42,416 --> 00:17:43,583
DONGFENG RULES

150
00:17:43,666 --> 00:17:45,958
THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S
AGENT FROM ABOVE WAS HERE

151
00:17:46,041 --> 00:17:47,416
INVINCIBLE THIRD CROWN PRINCE

152
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:48,958
DONGFENG RULES

153
00:17:49,041 --> 00:17:51,083
CHIEH KICKS ASS

154
00:17:54,291 --> 00:17:56,833
FUCK OFF BACK TO HELL

155
00:18:21,125 --> 00:18:23,666
Fuck. Eight won't be enough.

156
00:18:27,541 --> 00:18:28,625
Han Chieh.

157
00:18:32,916 --> 00:18:35,208
It's almost time. You should go home.

158
00:18:35,291 --> 00:18:37,125
Is there anything else I can do?

159
00:18:39,708 --> 00:18:42,500
You can go home and take your meds.
That's all I ask of you.

160
00:18:43,083 --> 00:18:44,083
Han Chieh.

161
00:18:45,250 --> 00:18:46,958
You think the wishing tree is dumb.

162
00:18:47,791 --> 00:18:49,750
Make a wish to the Third Crown Prince.

163
00:18:55,416 --> 00:18:57,416
Wish for victory tonight.

164
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:58,916
Okay?

165
00:19:03,333 --> 00:19:05,000
Whether he helps or not,

166
00:19:06,083 --> 00:19:07,458
I'm not going to beg.

167
00:19:10,458 --> 00:19:11,500
Also,

168
00:19:13,333 --> 00:19:15,208
having hope

169
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:18,583
only hurts more after it's gone.

170
00:19:39,208 --> 00:19:42,458
Old guard, what are you doing?
Why haven't you left yet?

171
00:19:46,875 --> 00:19:50,041
This is my home. Why should I leave?

172
00:19:50,541 --> 00:19:52,708
-Why are you staying?
-Why are you staying?

173
00:19:52,791 --> 00:19:54,583
The agent from above has to stay.

174
00:19:54,666 --> 00:19:58,291
Perfect. I'm applying to be
Lord Guan's agent from above.

175
00:19:58,375 --> 00:20:02,333
Have you met him?
He doesn't want you. Just drop it.

176
00:20:02,416 --> 00:20:04,833
If the old guard's staying,
I'm not going either.

177
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:06,291
Stay out of this.

178
00:20:07,416 --> 00:20:10,708
You have to go. Fighting is for men.

179
00:20:15,666 --> 00:20:17,083
Fried chicken.

180
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,875
Spareribs.

181
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,625
Spring rolls. Fried chicken.

182
00:20:27,041 --> 00:20:30,708
-I told you to wait at home, why--
-Spring rolls… Fried chicken.

183
00:20:32,083 --> 00:20:33,041
Spareribs.

184
00:20:34,458 --> 00:20:35,625
Spring rolls.

185
00:20:36,416 --> 00:20:37,291
Fried chicken.

186
00:20:39,708 --> 00:20:40,541
Fried chicken.

187
00:20:40,625 --> 00:20:41,458
Spare--

188
00:20:46,208 --> 00:20:48,500
I was getting takeout.
What am I doing here?

189
00:21:18,583 --> 00:21:19,500
Chieh?

190
00:21:20,958 --> 00:21:23,125
-Why am I back here?
-What's going on?

191
00:21:23,833 --> 00:21:25,583
They grew a conscience and came back?

192
00:21:26,166 --> 00:21:28,333
No, they've been possessed.

193
00:21:30,041 --> 00:21:31,541
Must be Wu Tien-chi's doing.

194
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:34,291
What's the bastard up to?

195
00:21:35,625 --> 00:21:37,958
Should everyone leave or go home?

196
00:21:40,458 --> 00:21:41,625
It's getting dark.

197
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:14,833
Come up, all of you.

198
00:22:22,875 --> 00:22:25,583
Go to Dongfeng Market.

199
00:22:25,666 --> 00:22:28,833
Say hello to Han Chieh for me.

200
00:22:29,458 --> 00:22:30,833
This time,

201
00:22:31,458 --> 00:22:34,041
no one can stop me

202
00:22:34,125 --> 00:22:38,250
from getting my demonic power back.

203
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,541
DONGFENG RESIDENTS ONLY

204
00:23:04,625 --> 00:23:05,583
Watch the steps.

205
00:23:07,875 --> 00:23:09,416
-Have some water.
-Here.

206
00:23:18,583 --> 00:23:19,416
Chieh.

207
00:23:20,666 --> 00:23:23,666
What's going on out there?
Are they coming?

208
00:23:26,083 --> 00:23:29,500
They should be here soon.
He's waiting for the moon to rise.

209
00:23:30,916 --> 00:23:34,333
Old guard, this will last all night.
Can you make it through?

210
00:23:34,416 --> 00:23:39,375
Hey, I've got your back.
I'll hold on as long as it takes.

211
00:23:41,041 --> 00:23:44,375
-Got a kitchen knife?
-What for? Killing ghosts?

212
00:23:44,875 --> 00:23:45,750
Yes.

213
00:23:46,708 --> 00:23:48,541
I only have a few milk caps left.

214
00:23:48,625 --> 00:23:51,583
I have to save them for the Demon King.

215
00:23:52,416 --> 00:23:57,041
Get the talismans I gave you before.
Putting them on weapons will help.

216
00:23:58,750 --> 00:24:01,291
Leafy, Sister Lo, Mei-na.

217
00:24:03,375 --> 00:24:05,625
Get everyone's keys.

218
00:24:05,708 --> 00:24:08,291
Get any supplies that we can use.

219
00:24:08,375 --> 00:24:10,500
Prepare for battle!

220
00:24:41,041 --> 00:24:43,958
We're going into battle.
What's with the idols and blankets?

221
00:24:44,041 --> 00:24:45,875
Han Chieh!

222
00:24:46,916 --> 00:24:48,250
Something's gotten in.

223
00:27:15,458 --> 00:27:17,458
-What gun is that?
-The gun of kindness.

224
00:27:17,541 --> 00:27:21,166
Kindness, my ass. Our guns and bullets
have been blessed by Lord Guan.

225
00:27:21,250 --> 00:27:23,500
Fu taught us.
Why aren't you using your milk caps?

226
00:27:23,583 --> 00:27:24,666
I wish I could.

227
00:27:58,666 --> 00:27:59,958
Get lost.

228
00:28:13,333 --> 00:28:14,708
Why are they leaving?

229
00:28:14,791 --> 00:28:16,416
-They're gone.
-What's going on?

230
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,833
Ms. Wang. Open the door.

231
00:28:19,416 --> 00:28:20,666
Open the door.

232
00:30:01,166 --> 00:30:03,833
Wu Tien-chi's coming.
Get in there and protect them.

233
00:30:03,916 --> 00:30:06,625
-Good thing Fu taught us this.
-And Chieh opened my third eye.

234
00:30:06,708 --> 00:30:10,625
Chieh, my heart's about to give out.
This is freaking terrifying.

235
00:30:17,666 --> 00:30:18,500
Where's Leafy?

236
00:30:19,208 --> 00:30:20,208
Where is she?

237
00:30:24,958 --> 00:30:26,083
Protect them.

238
00:30:31,125 --> 00:30:32,333
Have you seen Leafy?

239
00:30:32,833 --> 00:30:34,208
Isn't she with you?

240
00:30:40,041 --> 00:30:41,458
First floor.

241
00:30:47,583 --> 00:30:48,833
Let's get inside.

242
00:31:16,958 --> 00:31:17,875
Wu Tien-chi.

243
00:31:18,375 --> 00:31:19,458
Not so fast.

244
00:31:36,875 --> 00:31:39,333
You think those female ghosts
appeared in her home

245
00:31:39,416 --> 00:31:42,208
because her mom went to see
some lame feng shui master?

246
00:31:47,666 --> 00:31:49,250
Hi, Master Han. I'm Leafy.

247
00:31:49,333 --> 00:31:51,666
Someone put this under my dad's pillow.

248
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:53,333
A female ghost enchanted him.

249
00:31:57,666 --> 00:32:00,083
She has always been

250
00:32:00,833 --> 00:32:03,375
a pawn the Demon King placed beside you.

251
00:32:05,416 --> 00:32:07,333
I sent those ghosts
to her home every night

252
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:11,291
to blow demonic energy

253
00:32:12,291 --> 00:32:13,583
into her body.

254
00:32:14,791 --> 00:32:17,416
And refine her liver
into my demonic liver.

255
00:32:25,833 --> 00:32:28,208
It's been a while, little punk.

256
00:32:45,958 --> 00:32:49,208
You've matured since our last encounter.

257
00:32:51,875 --> 00:32:54,958
My punches hit harder now too.
Wanna find out for yourself?

258
00:32:59,625 --> 00:33:05,041
Compared to the other agents
I've fought in the past,

259
00:33:05,125 --> 00:33:09,125
the feel of your fist on my face
is so much more…

260
00:33:09,875 --> 00:33:11,208
satisfying.

261
00:33:11,291 --> 00:33:13,208
Cut the bullshit.

262
00:33:13,291 --> 00:33:17,000
You sucked Chen Chi-sha dry
and used Leafy to refine a liver

263
00:33:17,083 --> 00:33:18,625
to cultivate a new assistant,

264
00:33:19,333 --> 00:33:20,458
Wu Tien-chi, right?

265
00:33:20,541 --> 00:33:21,875
Wu Tien-chi?

266
00:33:23,875 --> 00:33:26,791
He's evil enough,
but doesn't have the talent.

267
00:33:26,875 --> 00:33:30,333
Surely a demonic liver
would be wasted on someone like him.

268
00:33:37,416 --> 00:33:39,541
I want you to have it.

269
00:33:41,208 --> 00:33:42,041
Me?

270
00:33:42,125 --> 00:33:45,375
You're younger than Chen Chi-sha
and stronger than Wu Tien-chi.

271
00:33:45,458 --> 00:33:47,041
Why not you?

272
00:33:50,583 --> 00:33:52,625
I'm so jealous of the Third Crown Prince.

273
00:33:52,708 --> 00:33:55,583
How did he find such a great assistant?

274
00:33:56,833 --> 00:33:58,041
Come work for me.

275
00:33:58,708 --> 00:34:01,458
I'll treat you better
than the Third Crown Prince does.

276
00:34:01,541 --> 00:34:03,916
You can have anything you want.

277
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:06,958
You can kill whoever you want.

278
00:34:11,541 --> 00:34:13,333
I prefer messing with scum like you.

279
00:34:14,166 --> 00:34:16,208
Like I prefer scraping shit off my shoe.

280
00:34:16,791 --> 00:34:19,916
So you only fight bad guys, right?

281
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,166
Hang on.

282
00:34:24,416 --> 00:34:26,875
You got your whole family killed.

283
00:34:28,708 --> 00:34:31,083
You're just as much of a bad guy.

284
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:35,875
That's why I'm
fucking slaving away for him.

285
00:34:38,416 --> 00:34:43,875
You know,
if you accept this demonic liver,

286
00:34:43,958 --> 00:34:46,791
you will gain immense demonic power,

287
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:50,833
and finally be rid
of the Third Crown Prince.

288
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:54,416
You can become my agent

289
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:57,416
and conquer all three realms with me.

290
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:59,083
Fuck you. I'm not interested.

291
00:35:02,333 --> 00:35:04,583
Do you think you have a choice?

292
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:09,833
It's too late.
The demonic liver has fully grown.

293
00:35:09,916 --> 00:35:13,666
It could burst out of her body
at any moment and rip her to pieces.

294
00:35:18,416 --> 00:35:20,666
Do you want her
to suffer such a tragic death?

295
00:35:32,083 --> 00:35:35,125
I'll trade livers,
but only on two conditions.

296
00:35:36,333 --> 00:35:38,416
Spare all the humans and ghosts here.

297
00:35:39,708 --> 00:35:40,583
And two.

298
00:35:44,250 --> 00:35:45,166
Give her my liver.

299
00:35:48,208 --> 00:35:49,333
She must live.

300
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:57,041
But she's already doomed to die.
Didn't you know?

301
00:35:59,250 --> 00:36:00,458
What do you mean?

302
00:36:01,375 --> 00:36:04,250
Her leukemia has spread.

303
00:36:05,416 --> 00:36:06,958
All this time,

304
00:36:07,041 --> 00:36:11,000
only the power of the demonic liver
has been keeping her alive.

305
00:36:15,041 --> 00:36:15,958
She didn't tell you?

306
00:36:20,916 --> 00:36:22,083
After I got sick,

307
00:36:22,166 --> 00:36:24,875
I started coming here to clear my head.

308
00:36:24,958 --> 00:36:27,666
You really think a wish
can bring about world peace?

309
00:36:28,625 --> 00:36:29,666
You never know.

310
00:36:29,750 --> 00:36:31,416
Han Chieh, smile.

311
00:36:32,666 --> 00:36:35,833
My love for the world
is woven into that wish.

312
00:36:41,375 --> 00:36:42,958
Every extra day is worth it.

313
00:36:47,041 --> 00:36:49,333
Okay, I'll do it.

314
00:36:53,791 --> 00:36:55,625
But you must give her my liver.

315
00:36:56,625 --> 00:36:58,708
I have to know she's still alive

316
00:36:59,666 --> 00:37:01,458
before I accept your demonic liver.

317
00:37:06,166 --> 00:37:08,416
I've killed so many people,

318
00:37:09,708 --> 00:37:11,750
but this is my first time saving one.

319
00:37:15,208 --> 00:37:16,958
Once you're working for me,

320
00:37:17,041 --> 00:37:19,375
don't ever talk to me like that again.

